article_title: Extenders Won't Delay Tax Season Start But Cuts Could Delay Tax Refunds

article_metadata.author: Kelly Phillips Erb

og.description: With the budget signed into law and tax extenders very nearly signed into law, how will tax season be affected? IRS Commissioner John Koskinen has some answers - and it's not all good news.
